  Anaïs stunned in the matching bright yellow bikini top and high-waisted bottoms. She accessorised her look with some gold necklaces layered over one another and a couple of delicate gold bracelets. The model wore her long blonde hair in loose waves and placed one hand on her midriff to pose. Anaïs is the daughter of Noel and his first wife, author Meg Mathews, 56. The couple married in Las Vegas in 1997 and divorced in 2001.  